/* Headline Rewind Resets Autosens */

"Rewind Resets Autosens" = "回卷重置 Autosens";

/* ”Rewind Resets Autosens” */
"This feature, enabled by default, resets the autosens ratio to neutral when you rewind your pump, on the assumption that this corresponds to a probable site change. Autosens will begin learning sensitivity anew from the time of the rewind, which may take up to 6 hours. If you usually rewind your pump independently of site changes, you may want to consider disabling this feature." = "此功能默认启用。当回卷（rewind）胰岛素泵时，会将 Autosens 比率重置为中性，基于回卷通常意味着更换注射部位这一假设。Autosens 将从回卷开始重新学习个体敏感系数，最多需要约 6 小时。如果你经常在不更换部位时执行回卷，建议关闭该功能。";

/* Headline "High Temptarget Raises Sensitivity" */
"High Temptarget Raises Sensitivity" = "高临时目标提高敏感性";

/* ”High Temptarget Raises Sensitivity" */
"Defaults to false. When set to true, raises sensitivity (lower sensitivity ratio) for temp targets set to >= 111. Synonym for exercise_mode. The higher your temp target above 110 will result in more sensitive (lower) ratios, e.g., temp target of 120 results in sensitivity ratio of 0.75, while 140 results in 0.6 (with default halfBasalTarget of 160)." = "
默认禁用。当设置为 \"true \"时，对设置为>=111的临时目标提高敏感系数（降低灵敏度比率）。与exercise_mode同义。你的临时目标越高于110，将导致更低的敏感系数，例如，临时目标为120，导致敏感系数为0.75，而140导致0.6（默认halfBasalTarget为160）。";

/* Headline ”Low Temptarget Lowers Sensitivity" */
"Low Temptarget Lowers Sensitivity" = "低临时目标降低敏感性";

/* ”Low Temptarget Lowers Sensitivity" */
"Defaults to false. When set to true, can lower sensitivity (higher sensitivity ratio) for temptargets <= 99. The lower your temp target below 100 will result in less sensitive (higher) ratios, e.g., temp target of 95 results in sensitivity ratio of 1.09, while 85 results in 1.33 (with default halfBasalTarget of 160)." = "默认禁用。启用后，当临时目标 ≤99 时降低敏感性（提高敏感性比率）。目标越低，比率越高，例如 95 时比率为 1.09，而 85 时为 1.33（默认 halfBasalTarget=160）。";

/* Headline ”Sensitivity Raises Target" */
"Sensitivity Raises Target" = "敏感性提高目标";

/* ”Sensitivity Raises Target" */
"When true, raises BG target when autosens detects sensitivity" = "启用后，当 Autosens 检测到敏感性增加时，提高 BG 目标值。";

/* Headline ”Resistance Lowers Target" */
"Resistance Lowers Target" = "抵抗降低目标值";

/* ”Resistance Lowers Target" */
"Defaults to false. When true, will lower BG target when autosens detects resistance" = "默认禁用。启用后，当 Autosens 检测到抵抗时，将降低 BG 目标。";

/* Headline ”Advanced Target Adjustments" */
"Advanced Target Adjustments" = "高级目标值调整";

/* ”Advanced Target Adjustments" */
"This feature was previously enabled by default but will now default to false (will NOT be enabled automatically) in oref0 0.6.0 and beyond. (There is no need for this with 0.6.0). This feature lowers oref0’s target BG automatically when current BG and eventualBG are high. This helps prevent and mitigate high BG, but automatically switches to low-temping to ensure that BG comes down smoothly toward your actual target. If you find this behavior too aggressive, you can disable this feature. If you do so, please let us know so we can better understand what settings work best for everyone." = "本功能此前默认启用，但在 oref0 0.6.0 起默认为关闭（不自动启用）。该功能在当前 BG 与预测 BG 偏高时自动降低目标 BG，从而帮助预防和缓解高血糖，并通过临时降低来平稳回落至设定目标。如果觉得行为太激进，可关闭此功能。如关闭，希望你反馈，以便社区了解更适合多数人的配置。";

/* Headline "Exercise Mode" */
"Exercise Mode" = "运动模式";

/* "Exercise Mode" */
"Defaults to false. When true, > 105 mg/dL high temp target adjusts sensitivityRatio for exercise_mode. Synonym for high_temptarget_raises_sensitivity" = "默认禁用。启用后，当临时目标 >105 mg/dL 时启用运动模式敏感性调整。等同于 high_temptarget_raises_sensitivity。";

/* Headline "Wide BG Target Range" */
"Wide BG Target Range" = "宽 BG 目标范围";

/* "Wide BG Target Range" */
"Defaults to false, which means by default only the low end of the pump’s BG target range is used as OpenAPS target. This is a safety feature to prevent too-wide targets and less-optimal outcomes. Therefore the higher end of the target range is used only for avoiding bolus wizard overcorrections. Use wide_bg_target_range: true to force neutral temps over a wider range of eventualBGs." = "默认禁用，即默认仅使用泵设定目标范围的低值作为 OpenAPS 目标，这是用于避免目标范围过宽导致控制效果变差的安全措施。高值仅用于避免大剂量向导过度校正。使用 wide_bg_target_range: true 可使更宽范围的预测 BG 使用中性临时基础。";

/* Headline "Skip Neutral Temps" */
"Skip Neutral Temps" = "跳过中性临时基础";

/* "Skip Neutral Temps" */
"Defaults to false, so that iAPS will set temps whenever it can, so it will be easier to see if the system is working, even when you are offline. This means iAPS will set a “neutral” temp (same as your default basal) if no adjustments are needed. This is an old setting for OpenAPS to have the options to minimise sounds and notifications from the 'rig', that may wake you up during the night." = "默认禁用，iAPS 会尽可能设置临时基础，这样即使离线也能看到系统是否运行。如不需要调整将设置中性临时基础（与默认基础相同）。这是早期 OpenAPS 的设置，用于减少设备提示音与通知避免夜间干扰。";

/* Headline "Unsuspend If No Temp” */
"Unsuspend If No Temp" = "无临时基础时解除暂停";

/* "Unsuspend If No Temp” */
"Many people occasionally forget to resume / unsuspend their pump after reconnecting it. If you’re one of them, and you are willing to reliably set a zero temp basal whenever suspending and disconnecting your pump, this feature has your back. If enabled, it will automatically resume / unsuspend the pump if you forget to do so before your zero temp expires. As long as the zero temp is still running, it will leave the pump suspended." = "许多人在重新连接泵后会忘记恢复输注。如果你属于此类用户，并且愿意在每次暂停或断开泵时可靠设置 0 临时基础，该功能可以帮助你。启用后，在 0 临时基础结束前若仍未恢复，系统会自动解除暂停。但在 0 临时基础还在运行时，泵仍保持暂停状态。";

/* Headline "Enable UAM" */
"Enable UAM" = "启用 UAM";

/* "Enable UAM" */
"With this option enabled, the SMB algorithm can recognize unannounced meals. This is helpful, if you forget to tell iAPS about your carbs or estimate your carbs wrong and the amount of entered carbs is wrong or if a meal with lots of fat and protein has a longer duration than expected. Without any carb entry, UAM can recognize fast glucose increasments caused by carbs, adrenaline, etc, and tries to adjust it with SMBs. This also works the opposite way: if there is a fast glucose decreasement, it can stop SMBs earlier." = "启用后，SMB 算法可识别未声明进餐。当忘记录入碳水、估算错误，或高脂高蛋白餐导致吸收延长时非常有用。在无碳水输入情况下，UAM 可识别由碳水、肾上腺素等导致的血糖快速上升并尝试通过 SMB 调整；反之，当血糖快速下降时会提前停止 SMB。";

/* Headline "Enable SMB With COB" */
"Enable SMB With COB" = "COB>0 时启用 SMB";

/* Enable SMB With COB" */
"This enables supermicrobolus (SMB) while carbs on board (COB) are positive." = "当 COB（活性碳水）为正时启用 SMB。";

/* Headline "Enable SMB With Temptarget” */
"Enable SMB With Temptarget" = "低临时目标启用 SMB";

/* "Enable SMB With Temptarget” */
"This enables supermicrobolus (SMB) with eating soon / low temp targets. With this feature enabled, any temporary target below 100mg/dL, such as a temp target of 99 (or 80, the typical eating soon target) will enable SMB." = "进餐前低临时目标启用 SMB。任何 <100 mg/dL 的临时目标（如 99 或典型进餐前目标 80）均会启用 SMB。";

/* Headline "Enable SMB Always" */
"Enable SMB Always" = "始终启用 SMB";

/* "Enable SMB Always" */
"Defaults to false. When true, always enable supermicrobolus (unless disabled by high temptarget)." = "
默认为禁用。当为 \"true \"时，总是启用SMB(除非被高的临时目标禁用)。";

/* Headline "Enable SMB After Carbs" */
"Enable SMB After Carbs" = "进食后启用 SMB";

/* "Enable SMB After Carbs" */
"Defaults to false. When true, enables supermicrobolus (SMB) for 6h after carbs, even with 0 carbs on board (COB)." = "默认关闭。启用后，在摄入碳水后的 6 小时内启用 SMB，即使 COB 为 0。";

/* Enable "Allow SMB With High Temptarget" */
"Allow SMB With High Temptarget" = "高临时目标也允许 SMB";

/* Headline "Allow SMB With High Temptarget" */
"Allow SMB With High Temptarget" = "高临时目标允许 SMB";

/* "Allow SMB With High Temptarget" */
"Defaults to false. When true, allows supermicrobolus (if otherwise enabled) even with high temp targets (> 100 mg/dl)." = "默认关闭，开启后当临时目标 >100 mg/dL 时也允许 SMB。";

/* Headline "Use Custom Peak Time” */
"Use Custom Peak Time" = "使用自定义达峰时间";

/* "Use Custom Peak Time” */
"Defaults to false. Setting to true allows changing insulinPeakTime" = "默认关闭，开启后可修改 insulinPeakTime。";

/* Headline "Suspend Zeros IOB” */
"Suspend Zeros IOB" = "暂停模式使用 0 IOB";

/* "Suspend Zeros IOB” */
"Default is false. Any existing temp basals during times the pump was suspended will be deleted and 0 temp basals to negate the profile basal rates during times pump is suspended will be added." = "默认关闭。泵暂停期间将移除已有临时基础，并以 0 临时基础覆盖配置基础速率。";

/* Headline "Max IOB" */
"Max IOB" = "最大 IOB";

/* "Max IOB" */
"Max IOB is the maximum amount of insulin on board from all sources – both basal (or SMB correction) and bolus insulin – that your loop is allowed to accumulate to treat higher-than-target BG. Unlike the other two OpenAPS safety settings (max_daily_safety_multiplier and current_basal_safety_multiplier), max_iob is set as a fixed number of units of insulin. As of now manual boluses are NOT limited by this setting. \n\n To test your basal rates during nighttime, you can modify the Max IOB setting to zero while in Closed Loop. This will enable low glucose suspend mode while testing your basal rates settings\n\n(Tip from https://www.loopandlearn.org/freeaps-x/#open-loop)." = "Max IOB 为系统允许累计的胰岛素总量，包括基础、SMB 校正和大剂量胰岛素，用于处理高血糖。不同于其他安全设置，其为固定单位值，目前手动大剂量不受此限制。\n\n夜间测试基础速率时，可在闭环模式下将 Max IOB 设为 0，启用低血糖暂停模式。\n\n（提示来自 https://www.loopandlearn.org/freeaps-x/#open-loop）";

/* Headline "Max Daily Safety Multiplier" */
"Max Daily Safety Multiplier" = "每日基础安全倍数上限";

/* "Max Daily Safety Multiplier" */
"This is an important OpenAPS safety limit. The default setting (which is unlikely to need adjusting) is 3. This means that OpenAPS will never be allowed to set a temporary basal rate that is more than 3x the highest hourly basal rate programmed in a user’s pump, or, if enabled, determined by autotune." = "重要安全参数，默认值为 3。即临时基础不会超过泵中最高小时基础速率的 3 倍（或 autotune 计算值）。一般无需调整。";

/* Headline "Current Basal Safety Multiplier" */
"Current Basal Safety Multiplier" = "当前基础安全倍数上限";

/* "Current Basal Safety Multiplier" */
"This is another important OpenAPS safety limit. The default setting (which is also unlikely to need adjusting) is 4. This means that OpenAPS will never be allowed to set a temporary basal rate that is more than 4x the current hourly basal rate programmed in a user’s pump, or, if enabled, determined by autotune." = "重要安全参数，默认值为 4。临时基础不会超过当前基础速率的 4 倍（或 autotune 值）。通常无需调整。";

/* Headline "Autosens Max" */
"Autosens Max" = "Autosens 最大系数";

/* "Autosens Max" */
"This is a multiplier cap for autosens (and autotune) to set a 20% max limit on how high the autosens ratio can be, which in turn determines how high autosens can adjust basals, how low it can adjust ISF, and how low it can set the BG target." = "Autosens（和 autotune）的最大倍数限制，限制敏感性提高最高 20%，影响基础、ISF 降低幅度以及 BG 目标降低幅度。";

/* Headline "Autosens Min" */
"Autosens Min" = "Autosens 最小系数";

/* "Autosens Min" */
"The other side of the autosens safety limits, putting a cap on how low autosens can adjust basals, and how high it can adjust ISF and BG targets." = "Autosens 安全限制的另一面，限制基础降低幅度的最大值，以及允许 ISF 和 BG 目标升高的上限。";

/* Headline "Half Basal Exercise Target" */
"Half Basal Exercise Target" = "半基础运动目标";

/* "Half Basal Exercise Target" */
"Set to a number, e.g. 160, which means when temp target is 160 mg/dL and exercise_mode=true, run 50% basal at this level (120 = 75%; 140 = 60%). This can be adjusted, to give you more control over your exercise modes." = "设为数值，例如 160，表示在临时目标 160 mg/dL 且启用运动模式时执行 50% 基础（120=75%，140=60%）。可调整以精细控制运动模式基础。";

/* Headline "Max COB" */
"Max COB" = "最大 COB";

/* "Max COB" */
"The default of maxCOB is 120. (If someone enters more carbs in one or multiple entries, iAPS will cap COB to maxCOB and keep it at maxCOB until the carbs entered above maxCOB have shown to be absorbed. Essentially, this just limits UAM as a safety cap against weird COB calculations due to fluky data.)" = "默认 Max COB 为 120。如碳水输入超过该值，系统将 COB 限制在 120 并保持，直到多余碳水显示已吸收。这主要用于避免异常数据导致错误 COB 计算。";

/* Headline "Bolus Snooze DIA Divisor" */
"Bolus Snooze DIA Divisor" = "大剂量暂停系数（基于 DIA）";

/* "Bolus Snooze DIA Divisor" */
"Bolus snooze is enacted after you do a meal bolus, so the loop won’t counteract with low temps when you’ve just eaten. The example here and default is 2; so a 3 hour DIA means that bolus snooze will be gradually phased out over 1.5 hours (3DIA/2)." = "餐前大剂量后会启用 Bolus snooze，防止闭环过早降低基础。默认值 2。如 DIA 为 3 小时，则 snooze 在 1.5 小时内渐进结束。";

/* Headline "Min 5m Carbimpact" */
"Min 5m Carbimpact" = "每 5 分钟最小碳水影响";

/* "Min 5m Carbimpact" */
"This is a setting for default carb absorption impact per 5 minutes. The default is an expected 8 mg/dL/5min. This affects how fast COB is decayed in situations when carb absorption is not visible in BG deviations. The default of 8 mg/dL/5min corresponds to a minimum carb absorption rate of 24g/hr at a CSF of 4 mg/dL/g." = "每 5 分钟碳水吸收对血糖影响的默认值（8 mg/dL/5min）。该值影响当 BG 曲线未体现碳水吸收时 COB 的衰减速率。默认对应最低吸收速率 24g/小时（CSF=4）。";

/* Headline "Autotune ISF Adjustment Fraction" */
"Autotune ISF Adjustment Fraction" = "Autotune ISF 调整系数";

/* "Autotune ISF Adjustment Fraction" */
"The default of 0.5 for this value keeps autotune ISF closer to pump ISF via a weighted average of fullNewISF and pumpISF. 1.0 allows full adjustment, 0 is no adjustment from pump ISF." = "默认值 0.5，通过 fullNewISF 与 pumpISF 加权平均，使 autotune 的 ISF 更接近泵设定。1 表示完全采用新值，0 表示不调整。";

/* Headline "Remaining Carbs Fraction" */
"Remaining Carbs Fraction" = "剩余碳水吸收比例";

/* "Remaining Carbs Fraction" */
"This is the fraction of carbs we’ll assume will absorb over 4h if we don’t yet see carb absorption." = "当未观察到吸收时，假设 4 小时内可被吸收的碳水比例。";

/* Headline "Remaining Carbs Cap" */
"Remaining Carbs Cap" = "剩余碳水吸收上限";

/* "Remaining Carbs Cap" */
"This is the amount of the maximum number of carbs we’ll assume will absorb over 4h if we don’t yet see carb absorption. Maximum 90" = "当未观察到吸收时，假设 4 小时内可吸收的最大碳水量，最大值 90。";

/* Headline ”Max SMB Basal Minutes" */
"Max SMB Basal Minutes" = "单次 SMB 最大基础时长";

/* ”Max SMB Basal Minutes" */
"Defaults to start at 30. This is the maximum minutes of basal that can be delivered as a single SMB with uncovered COB. This gives the ability to make SMB more aggressive if you choose. It is recommended that the value is set to start at 30, in line with the default, and if you choose to increase this value, do so in no more than 15 minute increments, keeping a close eye on the effects of the changes. It is not recommended to set this value higher than 90 mins, as this may affect the ability for the algorithm to safely zero temp. It is also recommended that pushover is used when setting the value to be greater than default, so that alerts are generated for any predicted lows or highs." = "默认值为 30 分钟，即单次 SMB 最大基础注射时长（未被 COB 覆盖时）。可适当增大以更激进。建议从 30 开始，每次增加不超过 15 分钟并观察效果。不建议超过 90 分钟，否则可能影响安全回退。建议配合推送提醒预测高/低血糖。";

/* Headline "Max UAM SMB Basal Minutes" */
"Max UAM SMB Basal Minutes" = "UAM SMB 最大基础时长";

/* "Max UAM SMB Basal Minutes" */
"Defaults to start at 30. This is the maximum minutes of basal that can be delivered by UAM as a single SMB when IOB exceeds COB. This gives the ability to make UAM more or less aggressive if you choose. It is recommended that the value is set to start at 30, in line with the default, and if you choose to increase this value, do so in no more than 15 minute increments, keeping a close eye on the effects of the changes. Reducing the value will cause UAM to dose less insulin for each SMB. It is not recommended to set this value higher than 60 mins, as this may affect the ability for the algorithm to safely zero temp. It is also recommended that pushover is used when setting the value to be greater than default, so that alerts are generated for any predicted lows or highs." = "默认值为 30。当 IOB>COB 时，UAM 单次 SMB 可提供的最大基础时长。可调整激进程度。建议从 30 开始，每次增加不超过 15 分钟。降低该值会减少单次 SMB 剂量。不建议超过 60 分钟，避免影响安全零基础能力。建议配合推送提醒。";

/* Headline "SMB Interval" */
"SMB Interval" = "SMB 间隔";

/* "SMB Interval" */
"Minimum duration in minutes for new SMB since last SMB or manual bolus" = "上一次 SMB 或手动大剂量后可执行新 SMB 的最短间隔时间（分钟）。";

/* Headline "Bolus Increment" */
"Bolus Increment" = "SMB 注射增量";

/* "Bolus Increment" */
"Smallest enacted SMB amount. Minimum amount for Omnipod pumps is 0.05 U, whereas for Medtronic pumps it differs for various models, from 0.025 U to 0.10 U. Please check the minimum bolus amount which can be delivered by your pump. The default value is 0.1." = "SMB 最小单位。Omnipod 为 0.05U，Medtronic 根据型号不同为 0.025U 到 0.10U，请确认你泵的最小剂量。默认 0.1U。";

/* Headline "Insulin Peak Time" */
"Insulin Peak Time" = "胰岛素作用达峰时间";

/* "Insulin Peak Time" */
"Time of maximum blood glucose lowering effect of insulin, in minutes. Beware: Oref assumes for ultra-rapid (Lyumjev) & rapid-acting (Fiasp) curves minimal (35 & 50 min) and maximal (100 & 120 min) applicable insulinPeakTimes. Using a custom insulinPeakTime outside these bounds will result in issues with iAPS, longer loop calculations and possible red loops." = "胰岛素产生最大降血糖作用的时间（分钟）。注意：Oref 假设 Lyumjev/Fiasp 最小/最大达峰时长分别为 35/50 和 100/120 分钟。超出范围可能导致 iAPS 计算异常和“红圈”提示。";

/* Headline "Carbs Req Threshold" */
"Carbs Req Threshold" = "碳水需求提醒阈值";

/* "Carbs Req Threshold" */
"Grams of carbsReq to trigger a pushover. Defaults to 1 (for 1 gram of carbohydrate). Can be increased if you only want to get Pushover for carbsReq at X threshold." = "触发碳水需求提醒的克数，默认 1g。可增大以只在较高需求时提醒。";

/* Headline "Noisy CGM Target Multiplier" */
"Noisy CGM Target Multiplier" = "噪声 CGM 目标倍数";

/* "Noisy CGM Target Multiplier" */
"Defaults to 1.3. Increase target by this amount when looping off raw/noisy CGM data" = "默认 1.3。当基于原始/噪声 CGM 数据闭环时按此比例提高目标。";

/* Headline "SMB DeliveryRatio" */
"SMB DeliveryRatio" = "SMB 注射比例";

/* SMB DeliveryRatio */
"Default value: 0.5 This is another key OpenAPS safety cap, and specifies what share of the total insulin required can be delivered as SMB. Increase this experimental value slowly and with caution." = "默认值 0.5，限制 SMB 在总需求胰岛素中的占比。建议谨慎且逐步调整。";

/* --- Dynamic ISF + CR Settings --- */
/* Headline "Adjust Dynamic ISF constant" */
"Adjust Dynamic ISF constant" = "动态 ISF 调整系数";

/* Adjust Dynamic ISF constant */
"Adjust Dynamic ISF constant" = "调整动态 ISF 常数";

/* Enable Dynamic ISF, Headline */
"Enable Dynamic ISF" = "启用动态 ISF";

/* Headline "Enable Dynamic ISF" */
"Enable Dynamic ISF" = "启用动态 ISF";

/* Enable Dynamic ISF */
"Calculate a new Insulin Sensitivity Setting (ISF) upon every loop cycle. The new ISF will be based on your current Glucose, total daily dose of insulin (TDD, past 24 hours of all delivered insulin) and an individual Adjustment Factor (recommendation to start with is 0.5 if using Sigmoid Function and 0.8 if not).\n\nAll of the Dynamic ISF and CR adjustments will be limited by your autosens.min/max limits." = "每个循环周期计算新的 ISF 值，基于当前 BG、过去 24 小时总胰岛素注射（TDD）和个人调整系数（Sigmoid 推荐 0.5，非 Sigmoid 推荐 0.8）。所有动态 ISF/CR 调整受 autosens.min/max 限制。";

/* Headline Enable Dynamic CR */
"Enable Dynamic CR" = "启用动态 CR";

/* Enable Dynamic CR */
"Use Dynamic CR. The dynamic ratio will be used for CR as follows:\n\n When ratio > 1:  dynCR = (newRatio - 1) / 2 + 1.\nWhen ratio < 1: dynCR = CR/dynCR.\n\nDon't use toghether with a high Insulin Fraction (> 2)" = "使用动态 CR：\n\n当比率 >1 时：dynCR = (newRatio - 1) / 2 + 1\n当比率 <1 时：dynCR = CR / dynCR\n\n不要与高 Insulin Fraction（>2）同时使用。";

/* Enable Dyn ISF */
"Activate Dynamic Sensitivity (ISF)" = "激活动态敏感性（ISF）";

/* Enable Dyn CR */
"Activate Dynamic Carb Ratio (CR)" = "激活动态碳水比（CR）";

/* Headline "Adjust Dynamic ISF constant" */
"Adjust Dynamic ISF constant" = "调整动态 ISF 常数";

/* Adjust Dynamic ISF constant */
"Individual adjustment of the computed dynamic ratios. Default is 0.5. The higher the value, the larger the correction of your ISF/CR will be for a high or a low blood glucose. Maximum/minumum correction is determined by the Autosens min/max settings.\n\nFor Sigmoid function an adjustment factor of 0.4 - 0.5 is recommended to begin with.\n\nFor the logaritmic formula there is less consensus, but starting around 0.8 is probably appropiate for most adult users. For younger users it's recommended to start even lower when using logaritmic formula, to avoid overly aggressive treatment." = "对动态比率进行个体调整。默认 0.5，值越高，ISF/CR 对高 BG 或低 BG 的修正越大，最大/最小修正由 Autosens min/max 决定。\n\nSigmoid 推荐初始值 0.4~0.5。\n\nLogaritmic 初始值建议约 0.8。年轻用户建议更低，以避免过度处理。";

/* Headline Use Sigmoid Function */
"Use Sigmoid Function" = "使用 Sigmoid 函数";


/* Which dyn ISF function to use */
"Formula" = "公式";

/* Extra Safety Features when using dyn ISF */
"Safety" = "安全";

/* Use Sigmoid Function */
"Use a sigmoid function for ISF (and for CR, when enabled), instead of the default Logarithmic formula. Requires the Dynamic ISF setting to be enabled in settings\n\nThe Adjustment setting adjusts the slope of the curve (Y: Dynamic ratio, X: Blood Glucose). A lower value ==> less steep == less aggressive.\n\nThe autosens.min/max settings determines both the max/min limits for the dynamic ratio AND how much the dynamic ratio is adjusted. If AF is the slope of the curve, the autosens.min/max is the height of the graph, the Y-interval, where Y: dynamic ratio. The curve will always have a sigmoid shape, no matter which autosens.min/max settings are used, meaning these settings have big consequences for the outcome of the computed dynamic ISF. Please be careful setting a too high autosens.max value. With a proper profile ISF setting, you will probably never need it to be higher than 1.5\n\nAn Autosens.max limit > 1.5 is not advisable when using the sigmoid function." =
"为 ISF（以及启用时的 CR）使用 S 型函数，而不是默认的对数公式。需要在设置中启用动态 ISF。\n\n“调整”参数会调整曲线斜率（Y：动态比例，X：血糖）。数值越小 ⇒ 曲线越平缓 ⇒ 调整越保守。\n\nautosens.min/max 用于同时决定动态比例的最大/最小范围，以及调整幅度。如果 AF 是曲线的斜率，那么 autosens.min/max 是图形的高度范围（Y 区间）。无论 autosens.min/max 如何设置，曲线始终为 S 型，这意味着它们会对计算出的动态 ISF 结果产生很大影响。请谨慎设置过高的 autosens.max。通常情况下，不需要超过 1.5。\n\n当使用 S 型函数时，不建议将 Autosens.max 设置超过 1.5。";

/* Headline Threshold Setting */
"Threshold Setting" = "阈值设置";

/* Dynamic ISF Setting Title */
"Minimum Threshold Setting" = "最低阈值设置";

/* Minimum Threshold Setting, Part 1 */
"This setting lets you choose a level below which no insulin will be given.\n\nThe threshold is using the largest amount of your threshold setting and the computed threshold:\n\nTarget Glucose - (Target Glucose - 40) / 2\n, here using mg/dl as glucose unit.\n\nFor example, if your Target Glucose is " =
"此设置允许你选择一个血糖值作为下限，在该值以下不会给胰岛素。\n\n系统会在你设置的阈值和计算阈值之间取较大的那个：\n\n目标血糖 - (目标血糖 - 40) / 2\n（此处血糖单位为 mg/dL）\n\n例如，如果你的目标血糖是 ";

/* Minimum Threshold Setting, Part 2 */
"the threshold will be " = "则阈值将为 ";

/* Minimum Threshold Setting, Part 3 */
"unless your threshold setting is set higher:" = "除非你设置的阈值更高：";

/* Threshold Table Columns Title */
"Setting" = "设置";

/* Threshold Table Columns Title */
"Threshold" = "阈值";

/* Dynamic settings View */
"Averages" = "平均值";

/* Dynamic settings View */
"Average ISF" = "平均 ISF";

/* Dynamic settings View */
"Average CR" = "平均 CR";

/* Dynamic settings View */
"Average CSF" = "平均 CSF";

/* Dynamic settings View */
"ISF: Insulin Sensitivity, CR: Carb Ratio,\nCSF: Carb Sensitivity = ISF/CR" =
"ISF：胰岛素敏感性，CR：碳水比例，\nCSF：碳水敏感性 = ISF/CR";

/* Header */
"Calculator settings" = "计算器设置";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Use alternate Bolus Calculator" = "使用替代注射计算器";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Use Bolus Calculator" = "使用注射计算器";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Depending on your settings the Swift bolus calculator is using data from the OpenAPS glucose predictions and/or from IOB, COB, glucose trend, current gluccose and target glucose. At the end of the calculation a custom factor is applied (default 0.8).\n\nYou can also have the option in your bolus calculator to apply another (!) customizable factor at the end of the calculation which could be useful for fatty meals, e.g Pizza (default 0.7).\n\nThe bolus calculator is NOT using the OpenAPS variable \"insulinRequired\", made for SMBs." =
"根据你的设置，Swift 注射计算器会使用 OpenAPS 血糖预测和/或 IOB、COB、血糖趋势、当前血糖和目标血糖。计算结束时会应用一个自定义系数（默认 0.8）。\n\n你也可以启用另一个可配置系数，用于高脂餐，例如披萨（默认 0.7）。\n\n该计算器不会使用 OpenAPS 中用于 SMB 的变量 \"insulinRequired\"。";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Adjustment" = "调整";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Use OpenAPS glucose predictions" = "使用 OpenAPS 血糖预测";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Fatty Meals" = "高脂餐";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"Apply factor for fatty meals" = "对高脂餐应用系数";

/* Bolus Calculator Footer */
"The new alternate bolus calculator is another approach to the default bolus calculator in iAPS. If the toggle is on you use this bolus calculator and not the original iAPS calculator. At the end of the calculation a custom factor is applied as it is supposed to be when using smbs (default 0.8).\n\nYou can also add the option in your bolus calculator to apply another (!) customizable factor at the end of the calculation which could be useful for fatty meals, e.g Pizza (default 0.7)." =
"新的替代注射计算器是不同于 iAPS 默认计算器的另一种方案。启用后，你将使用该计算器而非原始版本。计算结束时会应用一个自定义系数（默认 0.8）。\n\n你还可以启用另一个可配置系数，这对披萨等高脂餐可能有用（默认 0.7）。";

/* Bolus Calculator Setting */
"1. Use the OpenAPS eventual glucose prediction for computing the insulin recommended. This setting will enable the \"old\" calculator. On by default.\n\n2. Use the OpenAPS minPredBG prediction as a complementary safety guard rail, not allowing the glucose prediction to descend below your threshold. This setting can be used together with or without the eventual glucose. On by default" =
"1. 使用 OpenAPS 最终血糖预测来计算建议胰岛素剂量。启用此项将使用“旧版”计算器，默认开启。\n\n2. 使用 OpenAPS minPredBG 作为辅助安全限制，不允许预测血糖低于你的阈值。该设置可与最终血糖预测一同使用，也可单独使用，默认开启。";

/* Settings Section */
"Extra Features" = "额外功能";

/* Header */
"UI/UX Settings" = "UI/UX 设置";

/* UI/UX option */
"Display Predictions" = "显示预测";

/* UI/UX option */
"Smaller iPhone Screens" = "小屏幕优化";

/* UI/UX option */
"Display and allow Fat and Protein entries" = "显示并允许录入脂肪与蛋白质";

/* UI/UX option */
"Add Meal View settings " = "添加餐食视图设置";

/* UI/UX option */
